description: Greenhawk Resources Inc. operates as a mineral exploration company in Greenland. It holds 100% interest in two mineral exploration licenses and one prospecting license in the Storo Gold Project. The company was formerly known as Cryptologic Corp. and changed its name to Greenhawk Resources Inc. in May 2021. Greenhawk Resources Inc. is headquartered in Toronto, Canada.
